</div>
</div>
</div>
</div><div class="sect1">
<h2 id="50">2. Registering with Masterpayment</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>You have to <a href="https://www.masterpayment.com/en/auth/register" target="_blank" rel="noopener">register</a> before being able to use Masterpayment. You will receive the access data that you need for setting up Masterpayment in plentymarkets.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div><div class="sect1">
<h2 id="60">3. Setting up Masterpayment in plentymarkets</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Proceed as described below to set up the interface to Masterpayment.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Setting up the interface to Masterpayment:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>System » Orders » Payment » Methods</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Place a check mark next to the setting <strong>Also show inactive</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Open the folder <strong>International</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Masterpayment</strong>.<br>
→ The <strong>Interface</strong> tab will open.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Expand the client.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Carry out the settings as desired. Pay attention to the information given in <a href="#table-setup-masterpayment-interface">Table 1</a>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> the settings.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
